    <item>
      <title>中国出口限制导致镓价格上涨一倍多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/critical-metal-hit-by-china-curbs-has-more-than-doubled-in-price</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国的出口限制限制了全球供应，并损害了用于一系列高科技应用的金属的买家，镓的价格接近 2011 年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/critical-metal-hit-by-china-curbs-has-more-than-doubled-in-price</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 12:01:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
